The paper deals with generating 3D shapes, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and computer graphics (cs.GR). The use of deep neural networks and autoencoders suggests that the paper may also fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions single-view 3D reconstruction, which is a task that involves natural language processing (cs.CL) techniques.
